flowchart TD
    A[Contact Enrolled]
    A --> B{Wait 1 Day}
    B --> C[Send Email 1: Welcome]
    C --> D{Email 1 Engaged? (Opened/Clicked)}
    D -- Yes --> E{Wait 2 Days}
    D -- No --> F[End Campaign: No E1 Engagement]

    E --> G[Send Email 2: Product Info]
    G --> H{Email 2 Engaged? (Opened/Clicked)}
    H -- Yes --> I{Wait 3 Days}
    H -- No --> J[End Campaign: No E2 Engagement]

    I --> K[Send Email 3: Special Offer]
    K --> L{Email 3 Engaged? (Opened/Clicked)}
    L -- Yes --> M[End Campaign: Converted/Engaged]
    L -- No --> N[End Campaign: No E3 Engagement]